title: Filipe Ortiz joins Arnette Skate Team
description:
Arnette is proud to announce the addition of skateboarder Filipe Ortiz to the family.

This was shot during an East Coast skate trip that took the crew from Raleigh, NC, through Washington, D.C. and up to NYC to film the next set of episodes for Arnette's Multiple Personality Disorder series.

Watch for Filipe, along with Pat Duffy, Willy Santos, Danny Supa, Luis Tolentino, Sierra Fellers, Mark Appleyard, Filipe Ortiz, Scott Decenzo and Ryan Decenzo, to be featured in the Multiple Personality Disorder series later this year.
